sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as Customer
  participant C as Client (Web/Web Mobile/Mobile)
  participant P as Payment API
  participant O as Orchestrator
  participant A as Provider A
  participant B as Provider B (Fallback)

  U->>C: Submit order and payment method
  C->>P: Create payment (Idempotency-Key)
  P->>O: Validate + route request
  O->>A: Authorize (card / PayPal / Apple Pay)
  A-->>O: Soft decline (technical)
  O->>B: Fallback authorization
  B-->>O: Approved
  O-->>P: Authorized
  P-->>C: Payment status = authorized
  C-->>U: Show confirmation
